title: BRIEF-Nathan Miller Says Urge Destination Maternity Shareholders To Vote “For” Election Of His Nominees - SEC Filing
text:
April 27, 2018 / 7:47 PM / Updated 12 minutes ago BRIEF-Nathan Miller Says Urge Destination Maternity Shareholders To Vote “For” Election Of His Nominees - SEC Filing Reuters Staff 1 Min Read
April 27 (Reuters) - Destination Maternity Corp:
* NATHAN MILLER - URGE DESTINATION MATERNITY SHAREHOLDERS TO VOTE “FOR” ELECTION OF HOLLY ALDEN, CHRISTOPHER MORGAN TO SERVE AS DIRECTORS - SEC FILING
* NATHAN MILLER SAYS URGE DESTINATION MATERNITY SHAREHOLDERS TO VOTE “FOR” ELECTION OF MARLA RYAN AND ANNE-CHARLOTTE WINDAL TO SERVE AS DIRECTORS Source text: ( bit.ly/2HyUDCs ) Further company coverage:
